description: WATCH ONLINE and get more updates and new courses on http://Online-Courses.Club Title: How to Master Adobe Camera RAW (ACR) in Photoshop (UPDATED) Publisher: PHLearn Release: 2018 Website: https://phlearn.com/tutorial/adobe-camera-raw-photoshop/ Author: PHLearn Duration: 03 h 49 m Skill Level: Description: Processing RAW files requires specific software that will allow us to interpret the complex information within. Think of Photoshop as your photo editor, and Adobe Camera RAW as your photo developer. In this tutorial, you’ll learn to use Adobe Camera Raw to adjust white balance, recover details in the highlights and shadows, remove minor distractions, create HDR images, and to work seamlessly with Photoshop so that you can go back at anytime to make changes or adjustments
